Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.84,0:00:43.89,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Why not 闘い得た　絆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:52.52,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Just now　この手の中で　熱く輝け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.39,0:01:05.20,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}One in a seven billion の憂鬱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.38,0:01:10.76,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Someday 世界が終わる日が　来たって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.90,0:01:15.96,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}So，What？　1ミリの悔いもない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.13,0:01:21.68,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Say， yeah！！　一筋に走る流れ星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.86,0:01:24.34,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}鼓動ドキドキ止まれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.50,0:01:29.09,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}迷いも全部　蹴っ飛ばせ！！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.28,0:01:34.61,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}宇宙に　抱かれし　蒼い地球
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.77,0:01:39.88,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}いつも心に描く　エリシオン
